Just concluded a research and PoC rust implementation I think y'all would love to explore;

exploring the technical feasibility and performance implications of integrating the RISC-V instruction set architecture with the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM).

The main goal was run Rust written smart contract, but haven't gotten there yet... Smart contract for the variant of the EVM is still rewritten in RISCV Assemble;

